.SH NAME
shelly-cloud-events - Subscribe to real-time cloud events


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBshelly cloud events [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Subscribe to real-time events from the Shelly Cloud via WebSocket.

.PP
Displays events as they arrive from your cloud-connected devices.
Press Ctrl+C to stop listening.

.PP
Event types:
  Shelly:StatusOnChange  - Device status changed
  Shelly:Settings        - Device settings changed
  Shelly:Online          - Device came online/offline


.SH OPTIONS
\fB--device\fP=""
	Filter by device ID

.PP
\fB--event\fP=""
	Filter by event type

.PP
\fB--format\fP="text"
	Output format (text, json)

.PP
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for events

.PP
\fB--raw\fP[=false]
	Output raw JSON messages


